1. Sasha cooked food. So did I.
2. He won't buy an expensive TV set. Neither will Sasha.
3. Anna is at school. So is he.
4. He came home at two o'clock. So did I.
5. He didn't come home at three. Neither did we.
6. You didn't go to the restaurant. Neither did we.
7. I watched an interesting film. So did Andrew.
8. You would like to buy a new flat. So would I.
9. Tom will be happy. So will she.
10. I wasn't busy. Neither was he.
11. I would like to write a letter to him. So would she.
